		<h2>Ellenwood Lake</h2>
		<h3>How to Find Us</h3>
			<dl>
				<dt>Civic Address:</dt>
				<dd>1888 Mood Rd, Deerfield</dd>
				<dd>Ellenwood Lake Provincial Park is located just 19 km (12 mi.) northeast of Yarmouth and 1.6 km (1 mi.) south of Deerfield. Exit 34 off Highway 101, proceed 6.5 km (4 mi.) along Route 340. Follow signs to the park entrance.</dd>
			</dl>
